<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="besides-adv">besides <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bɪ'saɪdz/    美 /bɪ'saɪdz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>况且；此外：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’m too busy to go for a walk; besides, it is too late.
我太忙了，没时间散步，况且天也太晚了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Bicycling is good exercise; except, it does not pollute the air.    （2012 湖南改 改错）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. except → besides  </p></div>